---
title: Apricot-Dijon Double Pork Chops with Roasted Apple and Fennel Salad
description: Roasted fennel and apple take centre stage in this elegant pork chop dinner. The subtle anise flavour of fennel adds a "je ne sais quoi" that marries well with apricot-Dijon smothered pork chops.
